{
  "texts": [
    "This detailed account of our methodology enables other researchers to replicate our experiments and build upon our findings.",
    "We have evaluated open-source and closed-source LLMs, ensuring that researchers with access to either model type can reproduce our results.",
    "Furthermore, to facilitate further research and promote transparency, we have committed to making all prompts and codes publicly available in our codebase.",
    "This will enable other researchers to reproduce our experiments and verify our results.",
    "By taking these steps, we aim to ensure that our research is transparent and reproducible and contributes to the broader understanding of LLMs and their potential in addressing complex, real-world tasks."
  ]
}